          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<p>Why Epic Gear Pros?<\/p>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_rGkjwd": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At <strong>Epic Gear Pros<\/strong>, we believe that play is the foundation for learning. That’s why we’ve crafted our gear blocks to do more than entertain—they inspire creativity, problem-solving, and motor skills development in children. Designed with busy moms in mind, our products are safe, fun, and built to support your child's growth. We’re passionate about helping you nurture your child’s potential, one block at a time.<\/p><p><\/p>"
          }
        },
        "button_n8Nb86": {
